problem_text_en: As shown in the figure, it is known that the radius of ⊙O is N_0, the central angles of chords AB and CD are ∠AOB, ∠COD, and ∠AOB is complementary to ∠COD, chord CD = N_1, then the length of chord AB is ()
raw_answer: 解:解:如图,延长AO交⊙O于点E,连接BE,则∠AOB+∠BOE=180°,又∵∠AOB+∠COD=180°,∴∠BOE=∠COD,∴BE=CD,∵AE为⊙O的直径,∴∠ABE=90°,∴AB=√{AE^{2}-BE^{2}}=√{10^{2}-8^{2}}=6,故选:A．
